svapna-&#347;&#299;lasya — of one who sleeps; <A HREF=/bg/6/16><B>BG 6.16</B></A><BR>adharma-&#347;&#299;lasya — of one who is engaged in irreligion; <A HREF=/sb/3/5/3><B>SB 3.5.3</B></A><BR>dharma-&#347;&#299;lasya — who were strictly attached to religious principles; <A HREF=/sb/10/1/2><B>SB 10.1.2</B></A><BR>ati-svapna-&#347;&#299;lasya — of one who dreams too much in sleep; <A HREF=/cc/antya/8/67-68><B>CC Antya 8.67-68</B></A><BR></BODY></HTML>